17:16.200 --> 17:21.000
have done updates on a weekly basis at least, and only when I'm not, you know,

17:21.000 --> 17:29.100
obviously in need of production, is so that those sort of problems get flushed out by some people who are more risk tolerant,

17:29.100 --> 17:33.000
