18:06.400 --> 18:11.400
they'll end up running into problems. And I've had to help a lot of people fix broken Arch installs

18:11.400 --> 18:15.500
just because they went, you know, five weeks without updating and then things didn't work.

18:15.500 --> 18:22.700
